description:
Clean, comfortable, quiet one bedroom apartment with a cosy sitting  area to relax after a long day It fits two, and is located on a quiet street, surrounded by Caribbean kitchens, supermarkets  all major subway lines.

A home away from home.

Sitting area, tv,kitchen and bathroom.

The quietness and the food..... yummy.

Public transit 2 short blocks to the 2 and 5 trains. Plus taxi service 24/7.
name: Enjoy the comfort of Clemina's room
